spec_data.Name: perl-MooseX-Attribute-Chained
spec_data.Description:
MooseX::Attribute::Chained is a Moose Trait which allows for method
chaining on accessors by returning $self on write/set operations.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 01:44:19 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Attribute that returns the instance to allow for chaining
